Imports: boot, stats
Depends: R (>= 3.6.2), rcdd (>= 1.2)
Title: Simulating from the Polya Posterior
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Glen", family = "Meeden",
    email = "gmeeden@umn.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
